    Class that merges data from the vehicle and the map. The class finds optimal stops for the trip, among other things. Created by: Tim Kerschbaumer Project: Milestone Date: 2014-09-27 Time: 19:27 Last Edit: 2014-10-29

      • getMilestoneSuggestions

        public void getMilestoneSuggestions(IMilestone.Category category)
        This method is used to find pauses in driving mode. It will automatically send the found milestone to the handler passed when creating a NavigationModel. If no milestone is found this an error message will be passed to the handler. To Accept or decline the found milestone call "acceptMilestone". To Cancel the search call "cancelMilestoneSearch".
        Parameters:
        category - the category the milestone to be search for has to have.
